{"tid":1908041,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"珍惜生命 勿食魚米","createTime":"2020-03-03T04:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-03T10:13:18.000Z","uid":351722,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff4dd8b2caa88a7d74df48bedd27ab1c9dce5e6","tid":1908041,"uid":351722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:06:06.000Z","msg":"尋日食完嬲到忍唔住開ac<br />\n是咁的, 大家如果想食魚生先好去魚米<br />\n尋日我同朋友都叫左鯇魚腩米線, 但兩條都唔熟<br />\n所以通知職員, 當時佢地話重整一條比我地<br />\n犀利喇, 第3條都係唔熟<br />\n生到一忽忽透明<br />\n個廚師仲堅持係熟<br />\n(佢話跟足公司指示煮左5分鐘,所以所有佢煮出黎既魚都一定係熟,聽完依個解釋即刻超嬲）<br />\n真係我目前去過最差既餐廳<br />\n先不談味道如何, 最基本要煮熟都做唔到<br />\n個廚師又黑人憎 咁都話係熟同話條魚係正常<br />\n間野真係好L危險<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W4WNjCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW4WNjCD.jpg&h=9068b43a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我勸大家若珍惜生命, 真係唔好再食魚米"},{"pid":"8910f5e2c77b2f043678156abffde9367046bfd5","tid":1908041,"uid":213877,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:12:54.000Z","msg":"黃定籃？"},{"pid":"d34250d90fbba68a1d1c5806e4b518b218c26607","tid":1908041,"uid":186177,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:13:41.000Z","msg":"魚米劣到我阿媽都唔食"},{"pid":"451bda9d1da3bbb4beee7ace425f5b8500056d91","tid":1908041,"uid":85774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"魚米係大家樂嫁 ！"},{"pid":"9e6efb394028c132b83c05281d3eb65204f0a144","tid":1908041,"uid":60279,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:19:47.000Z","msg":"邊FUCK唔熟?<br />\n中間紅色果D好正常WOR<br />\n邊到透明? 不如你圈一圈出黎"},{"pid":"adaa35a6d39eaffd43e57572049aeef7a4a7f93a","tid":1908041,"uid":42435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-03T04:21:46.000Z","msg":"N 年冇食"},{"pid":"b916173162e4c7233a6acdad8d2ed04016c94555","tid":1908041,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"9e6efb394028c132b83c05281d3eb65204f0a144","tid":1908041,"uid":60279,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"c